402
00:15:06,976 --> 00:15:08,827
Oh, maybe she'll regret
taking you for granted

403
00:15:08,913 --> 00:15:11,156
when she's old and alone
in that big house

404
00:15:11,242 --> 00:15:14,250
and realizes all that money
can't keep her warm.

405
00:15:14,607 --> 00:15:16,289
