for you!

427
00:16:06,703 --> 00:16:08,688
Oh, Jay, you
don't know how much this means to me!

428
00:16:08,774 --> 00:16:10,875
Lily, you... you have
to apologize to Christina.

429
00:16:10,961 --> 00:16:11,977
That's right.

430
00:16:12,063 --> 00:16:14,180
Don't be like me and Cam
and Sergei and Alexei.

431
00:16:14,266 --> 00:16:16,031
Pride is poison!
Yes, open your heart!

432
00:16:16,117 --> 00:16:17,688
