433
00:16:17,774 --> 00:16:19,357
Jay...

434
00:16:19,443 --> 00:16:21,352
So, nobody's
wondering why Uncle Phil

435
00:16:21,445 --> 00:16:23,359
is starring
in a laundromat movie?

436
00:16:25,929 --> 00:16:28,055
N-No-o-o-o!

437
00:16:43,946 --> 00:16:45,195
So?

438
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:46,430
It's...

439
00:16:46,515 --> 00:16:47,865
not very good.

440
00:16:47,950 --> 00:16:49,860
