a sob in the cut

447
00:16:59,908 --> 00:17:01,759
because my boom operator
was undermining me.

448
00:17:01,845 --> 00:17:04,094
You had an astonishingly
toxic set.

449
00:17:04,569 --> 00:17:06,156
Listen, Manny,
if I was your dad,

450
00:17:06,242 --> 00:17:07,848
