00:17:17,111 --> 00:17:19,571
I-I want to see
how this ends.

458
00:17:20,209 --> 00:17:21,625
Thanks, Phil.

459
00:17:21,711 --> 00:17:23,227
I would like
to keep trying,

460
00:17:23,313 --> 00:17:24,729
